Chao-Bunge species richness estimator

This function implements the species richness estimation procedure outlined in Chao & Bunge (2002).

chao_bunge(data, cutoff = 10, print = TRUE, answers = FALSE)

Arguments

data

The sample frequency count table for the population of interest. See dataset apples for sample formatting.
cutoff

The maximum frequency to use in fitting.
print

Logical: whether the results should be printed to screen.
answers

Should the answers be returned as a list?

Value

The results of the estimator, including standard error.

Examples






















chao_bunge(apples)
